# PROMPT PENULISAN BUKU CRYPTOCURRENCY
## "CRYPTOCURRENCY: DARI NOL HINGGA MAHIR"

---

## **BAGIAN I: FONDASI CRYPTOCURRENCY**

### **BAB 1: PENGENALAN DUNIA DIGITAL CURRENCY**
**Prompt:**
```
Tuliskan BAB 1 untuk buku cryptocurrency dengan judul "Pengenalan Dunia Digital Currency". 
Target: Pemula yang belum mengenal cryptocurrency sama sekali.

Struktur yang harus dicakup:
- Definisi cryptocurrency yang mudah dipahami dengan analogi sehari-hari
- Perbandingan mendetail antara mata uang digital vs mata uang tradisional (tabel perbandingan)
- Penjelasan mengapa cryptocurrency penting di era digital (minimal 5 alasan konkret)
- Debunking 7 mitos umum tentang crypto beserta faktanya

Gaya penulisan: Conversational, mudah dipahami, gunakan analogi sederhana.
Panjang: 2000-2500 kata
Include: Contoh real-world, statistik terbaru, infografis konseptual
```

### **BAB 2: SEJARAH KELAHIRAN CRYPTOCURRENCY**  
**Prompt:**
```
Tuliskan BAB 2 tentang "Sejarah Kelahiran Cryptocurrency".
Fokus pada storytelling yang menarik tentang asal-usul crypto.

Struktur wajib:
- Latar belakang krisis finansial 2008 dan dampaknya terhadap kepercayaan sistem perbankan
- Misteri Satoshi Nakamoto: profil mendalam, teori identitas, motivasi di balik Bitcoin
- Analisis Bitcoin whitepaper (31 Oktober 2008) - penjelasan konsep kunci dalam bahasa sederhana
- Timeline detail perkembangan crypto 2009-2025 dengan milestone penting
- Cerita di balik transaksi Bitcoin pertama (pizza 10,000 BTC) dan maknanya

Gaya penulisan: Naratif seperti dokumenter, engaging, historically accurate
Panjang: 3000-3500 kata
Include: Timeline visual, quotes dari whitepaper, analisis dampak sejarah
```

### **BAB 3: TEKNOLOGI BLOCKCHAIN - TULANG PUNGGUNG CRYPTOCURRENCY**
**Prompt:**
```
Tuliskan BAB 3 tentang "Teknologi Blockchain" dengan pendekatan step-by-step yang mudah dipahami.

Struktur wajib:
- Konsep distributed ledger dengan analogi buku catatan komunal
- Cara kerja blockchain dijelaskan dalam 10 langkah sederhana dengan diagram konseptual
- Penjelasan cryptographic hashing dengan contoh SHA-256
- Mekanisme konsensus: Proof of Work vs Proof of Stake (perbandingan detail)
- Desentralisasi vs sentralisasi: keunggulan dan tantangan masing-masing

Gaya penulisan: Technical tapi accessible, banyak analogi visual
Panjang: 2500-3000 kata
Include: Diagram alur, contoh hash, perbandingan tabel PoW vs PoS
```

---

## **BAGIAN II: MEMAHAMI CRYPTOCURRENCY SECARA MENDALAM**

### **BAB 4: BITCOIN - CRYPTOCURRENCY PERTAMA**
**Prompt:**
```
Tuliskan BAB 4 tentang "Bitcoin - Cryptocurrency Pertama" sebagai deep dive ke Bitcoin.

Struktur wajib:
- Karakteristik unik Bitcoin: supply cap 21 juta, pembagian desimal, immutability
- Proses mining Bitcoin: dari hash rate hingga difficulty adjustment
- Fenomena Bitcoin halving: sejarah, dampak ekonomi, prediksi masa depan
- Tantangan skalabilitas: throughput TPS, ukuran blok, confirmation time
- Lightning Network sebagai layer 2 solution (penjelasan teknis dan implementasi)

Gaya penulisan: Technical depth dengan penjelasan praktis
Panjang: 3500-4000 kata
Include: Chart halving history, mining difficulty graph, Lightning Network diagram
```

### **BAB 5: ETHEREUM DAN SMART CONTRACTS**
**Prompt:**
```
Tuliskan BAB 5 tentang "Ethereum dan Smart Contracts" dengan fokus pada inovasi beyond Bitcoin.

Struktur wajib:
- Vitalik Buterin: visi Ethereum sebagai "world computer"
- Konsep smart contract dengan 5 contoh use case praktis
- Ethereum Virtual Machine (EVM): cara kerja dan significance
- Ekosistem DeFi: AMM, lending, yield farming, top protocols
- NFT revolution: from CryptoKitties to digital art marketplace

Gaya penulisan: Innovation-focused, forward-looking
Panjang: 3500-4000 kata
Include: Smart contract code example, DeFi ecosystem map, NFT market stats
```

### **BAB 6: JENIS-JENIS CRYPTOCURRENCY**
**Prompt:**
```
Tuliskan BAB 6 tentang "Jenis-jenis Cryptocurrency" sebagai comprehensive categorization.

Struktur wajib:
Berdasarkan fungsi:
- Payment coins (Bitcoin, Litecoin, Bitcoin Cash) - analisis comparative
- Utility tokens (Ethereum, BNB, Chainlink) - use case analysis
- Stablecoins (USDT, USDC, DAI) - mechanisms dan backing
- Privacy coins (Monero, Zcash) - privacy technology comparison

Berdasarkan teknologi:
- Layer 1 protocols (Ethereum, Solana, Cardano)
- Layer 2 solutions (Polygon, Arbitrum, Optimism)
- Cross-chain bridges dan interoperability

Gaya penulisan: Categorical, analytical, comparison-heavy
Panjang: 4000-4500 kata
Include: Classification matrix, market cap comparison, technology comparison table
```

---

## **BAGIAN III: EKOSISTEM CRYPTOCURRENCY**

### **BAB 7: WALLET CRYPTOCURRENCY**
**Prompt:**
```
Tuliskan BAB 7 tentang "Wallet Cryptocurrency" dengan fokus praktis dan keamanan.

Struktur wajib:
- Jenis wallet: Hot vs Cold wallet (perbandingan keamanan vs convenience)
- Hardware wallet terbaik: Ledger, Trezor, review dan rekomendasi
- Software wallet: mobile, desktop, browser - review top 10
- Keamanan private key dan seed phrase: best practices, recovery procedures
- Multi-signature wallets: konsep, implementasi, use cases

Gaya penulisan: Practical guide, security-focused
Panjang: 3000-3500 kata
Include: Wallet comparison matrix, security checklist, setup guides
```

### **BAB 8: CRYPTOCURRENCY EXCHANGES**
**Prompt:**
```
Tuliskan BAB 8 tentang "Cryptocurrency Exchanges" dengan analisis mendalam pasar exchange.

Struktur wajib:
- CEX vs DEX: trade-offs, keunggulan/kelemahan masing-masing
- Cara memilih exchange: kriteria keamanan, likuiditas, fees, regulasi
- Trading pairs dan order types: market, limit, stop-loss explanation
- Fee structure: maker/taker, withdrawal fees, spread analysis
- Regulasi exchange global: compliance requirements, jurisdictional differences

Gaya penulisan: Analytical, decision-making focused
Panjang: 3500-4000 kata
Include: Exchange comparison table, fee analysis, regulatory landscape map
```

### **BAB 9: MINING DAN STAKING**
**Prompt:**
```
Tuliskan BAB 9 tentang "Mining dan Staking" dengan pendekatan teknis dan ekonomis.

Struktur wajib:
- Konsep mining: dari CPU ke ASIC evolution
- Hardware requirements: GPU vs ASIC, profitability calculation
- Mining pools vs solo mining: probability, variance, pool selection
- Proof of Stake mechanism: validators, slashing, rewards calculation
- Environmental impact: carbon footprint analysis, green alternatives

Gaya penulisan: Technical, economically aware
Panjang: 3000-3500 kata
Include: Mining profitability calculator, staking rewards comparison, environmental impact data
```

---

## **BAGIAN IV: STRATEGI DAN PRAKTIK**

### **BAB 10: ANALISIS CRYPTOCURRENCY**
**Prompt:**
```
Tuliskan BAB 10 tentang "Analisis Cryptocurrency" sebagai trading/investment guide.

Struktur wajib:
Technical Analysis:
- Chart patterns dalam crypto: head & shoulders, triangles, support/resistance
- Indikator teknikal: RSI, MACD, Bollinger Bands application to crypto
- Volume analysis dan market sentiment indicators

Fundamental Analysis:
- Tokenomics analysis: supply/demand dynamics, inflation/deflation models
- Team evaluation: track record, advisory board, community
- Adoption metrics: active addresses, transaction volume, developer activity
- Market sentiment tools: fear & greed index, social media analysis

Gaya penulisan: Educational, actionable
Panjang: 4000-4500 kata
Include: Chart examples, analysis frameworks, evaluation checklists
```

### **BAB 11: STRATEGI INVESTASI CRYPTOCURRENCY**
**Prompt:**
```
Tuliskan BAB 11 tentang "Strategi Investasi Cryptocurrency" dengan fokus risk management.

Struktur wajib:
- Dollar Cost Averaging (DCA): implementation, backtesting results
- HODLing vs Trading aktif: psychological factors, performance comparison
- Portfolio diversification: crypto allocation, correlation analysis
- Risk management: position sizing, stop-loss strategies, volatility management
- Tax implications: capital gains, staking rewards, DeFi complexity

Gaya penulisan: Strategic, risk-aware, data-driven
Panjang: 3500-4000 kata
Include: Strategy comparison table, risk assessment framework, tax planning guide
```

### **BAB 12: DeFi DAN APLIKASI LANJUTAN**
**Prompt:**
```
Tuliskan BAB 12 tentang "DeFi dan Aplikasi Lanjutan" untuk advanced users.

Struktur wajib:
- Yield farming dan liquidity mining: mechanism, risks, top protocols
- Lending/borrowing protocols: Aave, Compound, overcollateralization concept
- Decentralized Autonomous Organizations (DAOs): governance, participation
- GameFi dan Play-to-Earn: Axie Infinity model, sustainability analysis
- Metaverse dan virtual economies: land ownership, virtual assets

Gaya penulisan: Advanced, experimental, future-focused
Panjang: 4000-4500 kata
Include: DeFi protocol comparison, GameFi ecosystem map, DAO governance examples
```

